Package: cauda
Title: CAUDA - Causal Automated Directed Acyclic Graph Extractor
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-05-29
Authors@R: c(
  person("Aadi", "Soni", email = "mr.aadi.soni@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Professor", "Cox", role = "aut")
)
Maintainer: Aadi Soni <mr.aadi.soni@gmail.com>
Description: Enterprise-grade system for extracting causal relationships from
    academic papers, building directed acyclic graphs (DAGs), evaluating
    extraction quality with advanced statistical metrics, and providing
    publication-ready visualizations. Includes classical data analysis capabilities
    (correlation, causal learning, optimization) plus modern paper analysis with
    confidence-aware DAGs and quality assurance.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    bnlearn,
    igraph,
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra,
    reshape2,
    parallel
License: MIT
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
